      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HELLO PRETZEL (5) carved over from wide out and boxed on strongly to finish a nose away in second (30.47) behind Code Of Silence at Gosford. The form from her last run is stacking up nicely. Likely to feature again. LITTLE MIMI (4) was strongly supported last start when a short priced favourite and duly saluted winning by 0.8 lengths at Gunnedah in a handy 25.34. Has a tricky draw to overcome but in form and has the ability. Can make it two on the bounce. ZIPPING PERCAT (2) was safely held last time out, finishing eighth at Maitland over 450m behind Zipper Stride (25.95) in a Grade 5. Can measure up this time. ZIPPING ALONSO (3) was unplaced here last start but gets his chance to atone.",
